Shop Goldies

Modeling
May 1 2019

Moving to California scared me. Leaving Japan scared me. I had created such a small group of creators who loved to photograph together. When I came to Cali I was afraid I wouldn’t find that. But I decided to reach out to this amazing Photographer Isaiah E. KajumbaI. I saw his work and was absolutely amazed by his style of photography.! 

After a few weeks of getting settled, he reached out to me and asked If I wanted to shoot with him and this local store in Downtown Ventura.. Goldies. OF COURSE, I DID! 

I hadn’t modeled in over a month! I was so excited and nervous but I did it. Take a look at some highlights. 

If you have any questions or need some advice on what to buy, hit me up!
